strings: <voice_0x01000E5D><se_def>*: If you join us, we know the time has come to do the same...
<voice_0x01000E5F><se_def>*: ...Yes, I see. Is the dark energy escaping from the ruins a fence erected by two sorcerers?
<voice_0x01000E60><se_def>*: Therefore, one must defeat him before working with him. But how...? How can we dispel darkness?
<voice_0x01000E61><se_def>*: Wait And the magic glass of Arjun? It is said to dispel darkness
<voice_0x01000E62><se_def>*: can not be used for real
<voice_0x01000E63><se_def>*: If I remember correctly, but gamble?
